Appointment Table

AppointmentID (int, primary key)
PatientID (int, foreign key)
DoctorID (int, foreign key)
Date (datetime)
Reason (nvarchar)
Notes (nvarchar)

Patient Table

PatientID (int, primary key)
FirstName (nvarchar)
LastName (nvarchar)
DateOfBirth (date)
Gender (nvarchar)
Address (nvarchar)
Phone (nvarchar)

Doctor Table

DoctorID (int, primary key)
FirstName (nvarchar)
LastName (nvarchar)
Specialty (nvarchar)

VitalSigns Table

VitalSignsID (int, primary key)
AppointmentID (int, foreign key)
HeartRate (int)
BloodPressure (nvarchar)
Temperature (decimal)
RespiratoryRate (int)

Diagnosis Table

DiagnosisID (int, primary key)
AppointmentID (int, foreign key)
Description (nvarchar)
Code (nvarchar)
